NoteAddException
public class SequenceException
extends java.lang.Exception
implements NoteSequence

Thrown when an exception in a NoteSequence is encountered. Other exceptions extend this class and provide more specific information about the nature of the failure that occurred.

See Also:
NoteAddException, Serialized Form
